{
  "stem": "1938.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I first came to this first city what they put us together to send us to Germany, I looked around and I picked a girl from my town.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was a little older, very quiet and very-- and good disposition, you know, and a reputation.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I told her I would like to be your sister.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would like to be, whatever happens to us, that we have each other.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was smart enough this time to do this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were always together, sharing our little [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you know, cupboards, everything, put together the food.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were together until-- I'll tell you the story what happened to us, given I'm there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right now, we are just walking out in-- from this-- from our Grunberg.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were walking, and on the way, they took us to Helmbrechts, this is a [? church. ?] Well, they always put us mountains and lakes, whatever they thought maybe the Russians or the Americans could meet us, they were trying to avoid.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they were taking all this long distances for us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were walking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her name was Tzipora Margakevitch.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She's supposed to be in Haifa in Israel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were walking, and it was-- I-- I just say that everybody should have a faith, but special we had such a faith.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew that we we're going to survive with this condition, but still we-- we were thinking about walking, and walking, and walking, beside our pains and everything.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were walking in a little town, Helmbrechts.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They put us in a room, and there was no facilities for bathroom, for nothing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They put in the front a-- a pail, and that's-- and took us all naked.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
